<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>MK Protocol</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #111;
      color: #fff;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }
    h1 {
      color: gold;
      font-size: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .subtitle {
      color: gold;
      font-size: 16px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .slogan {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .menu {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .menu button {
      background-color: gold;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      font-size: 16px;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: black;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    .menu button:hover {
      background-color: #ffd700;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #aaa;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>MK</h1>
  <div class="subtitle">GOLD · AUTO · TRADE · VALUE NETWORKING</div>
  <div class="slogan">Real Value Connects Real People.</div>
  <div class="menu">
    <button>나의 흐름 보기</button>
    <button>내 흐름도 정리해보고 싶다면?</button>
    <button>MK Protocol 보기</button>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">“크게 도움이 되진 못하지만, 언제든 작은 연결이 되고 싶습니다.”</div>
</body>
</html>
